<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Scimitar" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Scimitar,</orth> a sword: <bibl n="shak. mv 2.1.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 1, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 1, 2</bibl>. <cit><quote>he dies upon my --'s sharp point,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 2, 91</bibl></cit> (consequently not a sabre with a convex edge).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>